name: AkitaDAO

methods.name: optinEscrow

args.name: asset
args.desc: The asset to be opted into

methods.desc: optin tells the contract to opt into an asa

desc:
The Akita DAO contract has several responsibilities:
[-] Manages the disbursement of the bones token
[x] Manages the content policy of the protocol
[-] Manages the minimum impact score to qualify for daily disbursement
[x] Sets the fee to post on akita social
[x] Sets the fee to react on akita social
[-] Sets the fee structure for Akita Staking
[x] Sets the fee structure for Akita Subscriptions
[-] Sets the fee structure for Akita NFT Listings
[-] Sets the fee structure for Akita NFT Shuffles
[-] Sets the fee structure for Akita Auctions
[-] Sets the fee structure for Akita Asset Swaps

version.desc: the version number of the DAO

contentPolicy.desc: the raw 36 byte content policy of the protocol

minimumRewardsImpact.desc: the minimum impact score to qualify for daily disbursement

akitaAppList.desc: the list of akita contract ids

pluginAppList.desc: the list of plugin contract ids

otherAppList.desc: the list of other contract ids we use

krbyPercentage.desc:
The percentage of total rewards allocated to krby expressed in the hundreds
eg. 3% is 300, 12.75% is 1275

executions.desc: Group hashes that the DAO has approved to be submitted

escrows.desc: named escrow accounts the DAO uses

sourceInfo.errorMessage: Escrow is not allowed to opt-in
Index access is out of bounds
can only call when not creating
